    "body": "Do you want to just show the stars, or should it also do something when you click on it? \r\n\r\nTo just show it you can use [the template](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/hits.html#struct-HitsTemplates) and loop over the stars until you have the right amount. ",
