    "body": "@Haroenv I just want to show stars of each item. I have an attribute names rating which has float value. How can I show stars with that float value of each item.? can you please share some code with me. I have seen that documentation but I did not get anything ng from there that I need. In \"hits\" template, I want to show the rating of each item with stars like I posted the picture above.\r\n\r\nThanks for reply 👍 waiting for next reply ....",
